cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.ET, cs.SY

The paper discusses a new computational approach to quantum neural networks that can achieve low-cost learning. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of quantum computing, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET). Finally, the proposed approach is capable of self-adaptation, which is a characteristic of autonomous systems (cs.SY).
